<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>We Are Closed - Sweet Crumbs Cake Bakery</title>
  <style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #3d2b24;
  background-color: #fff8f5;
}

.bakery-header {
  height: 64px;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0 28px;
  background: rgba(15, 12, 11, 0.84);
  color: white;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 40px 170px 1fr 120px;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 1000;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.menu-button {
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border: 0;
  background: transparent;
  display: grid;
  place-content: center;
  gap: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.menu-button span {
  width: 16px;
  height: 2px;
  background: white;
  display: block;
}

.bakery-logo {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  line-height: 1;
  text-align: center;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.logo-mark {
  display: block;
  font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0;
}

.logo-subtitle {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 3px;
  font-size: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: 1.8px;
  color: #cdbeb9;
}

.bakery-nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 54px;
}

.bakery-nav a {
  color: white;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.bakery-nav a:hover,
.bakery-nav a.active {
  color: #f1c0c6;
}

.outline-button {
  color: white;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  font-size: 0.62rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-align: center;
}

.closed-body {
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(61, 43, 36, 0.72), rgba(61, 43, 36, 0.72)),
    url('https://i1-e.pinimg.com/1200x/0d/0f/95/0d0f95f2b2d0f32a0d1c316e4a1b7388.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding-top: 64px;
}

.closed-page {
  min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.closed-container {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  max-width: 620px;
  width: 100%;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
}

.closed-container h1 {
  color: #8b3a4a;
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.closed-message,
.closed-text {
  color: #6b554c;
}

.hours-info,
.clock {
  background: #fff8f5;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}

.hours-info h2,
#current-time {
  color: #8b3a4a;
}

#current-time {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin: 0;
}

.closed-text a {
  color: #8b3a4a;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.closed-text a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.site-footer {
  background: #ead0cf;
  color: #3d2b24;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
}

.footer-logo {
  color: #3d2b24;
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.site-footer p {
  color: #6b5a52;
  margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  max-width: 520px;
}

.social-links {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.social-links a {
  width: 42px;
  height: 42px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(61, 43, 36, 0.28);
  border-radius: 50%;
  color: #3d2b24;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}

.social-links a:hover {
  background: #8b3a4a;
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.social-links svg {
  width: 21px;
  height: 21px;
  fill: none;
  stroke: currentColor;
  stroke-linecap: round;
  stroke-linejoin: round;
  stroke-width: 1.8;
}

.social-links a:nth-child(2) svg,
.social-links a:nth-child(3) svg {
  fill: currentColor;
  stroke: none;
}

.site-footer small {
  color: #9b8a7f;
}

main {
  padding-top: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .closed-container {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bakery-header {
    grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr 120px;
  }

  .bakery-nav {
    display: none;
  }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body class="closed-body">
  <header class="bakery-header">
    <button class="menu-button" aria-label="Open menu">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </button>
    <a href="/" class="bakery-logo">
      <span class="logo-mark">BAKERY</span>
      <span class="logo-subtitle">Sweet Crumbs</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="bakery-nav">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/services">Our Services</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="/contact" class="outline-button">Order Now</a>
  </header>

  <main class="closed-page">
    <section class="closed-container">
      <h1>We Are Currently Closed</h1>
      <p class="closed-message">
        Sweet Crumbs Cake Bakery is available during working hours only.
      </p>

      <div class="hours-info">
        <h2>Working Hours</h2>
        <p><strong>Monday - Friday:</strong> 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
        <p><strong>Weekends:</strong> Closed</p>
      </div>

      <p class="closed-text">
        Please come back during our working hours. For cake inquiries, email us at
        <a href="mailto:orders@sweetcrumbs.com">orders@sweetcrumbs.com</a>.
      </p>

      <div class="clock">
        <p id="current-time"></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a href="/" class="footer-logo">Sweet Crumbs</a>
    <p>Fresh cakes, pastries, and dessert tables for elegant celebrations.</p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="5"></rect><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1"></circle></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 8h3V4h-3c-3 0-5 2-5 5v3H6v4h3v5h4v-5h3l1-4h-4V9c0-.6.4-1 1-1z"></path></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Snapchat">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3c3 0 5 2.4 5 5.6v2.1c0 1.4 1.3 2.2 2.6 2.6-.6 1.5-2 2.3-3.6 2.5-.7 1.5-2 2.2-4 2.2s-3.3-.7-4-2.2c-1.6-.2-3-.9-3.6-2.5 1.3-.4 2.6-1.2 2.6-2.6V8.6C7 5.4 9 3 12 3z"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <small>&copy; 2026 Sweet Crumbs Cake Bakery. Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 5 PM.</small>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
